GeneralExplanation.Identifier: ORGANIZATION'S PROCESS USED TO REVIEW FORM 990
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: THE CPA PREPARING FORM 990 SENDS A DRAFT COPY TO THE EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR WHO IN TURN MAKES IT AVAILABLE TO THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS.
THE ORGANIZATION MONITORS AND ENFORCES COMPLIANCE WITH ITS WRITTEN CONFLICT OF INTEREST POLICY BY MEANS OF A QUESTIONNAIRE.

EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE ACTING ON BEHALF OF THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS CONDUCTS PERFORMANCE APPRAISAL AND COMPARISON WITH SALARY SURVEYS OF OTHER PENNSYLVANIA WORKFORCE ORGANIZATIONS. EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE THEN ASSESSES SALARY AND REPORTS TO THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS.
THE ORGANIZATION MAKES ITS GOVERNING DOCUMENTS, CONFLICT OF INTEREST POLICY AND FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AVAILABLE UPON REQUEST.
